### Регистрация ROLE_USER
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signUp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "senya",
  "fio": "Арсеня Мягков",
  "password": "senya123",
  "passwordConfirm": "senya123",
  "role": "USER"
}
### Регистрация ROLE_ADMIN
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signUp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "dd",
  "fio": "Leha Иванова",
  "password": "secret123",
  "passwordConfirm": "secret123",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### Регистрация ROLE_INSPECTOR
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signUp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "pasha",
  "fio": "Pasha Иванова",
  "password": "secret123",
